          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "description": "Create a worker service listing as multipart form-data. This matches the mobile flow: category/subcategory selection, work areas, availability, description, and gallery photos. Send `workAreas` and `availabilityRules` as JSON strings, and repeat the `images` key for multiple files.",
